  "general_provisions": "This bill modifies provisions involving land surveyors.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>updates statutory references;<hr><ltbullet>sets the standard for future uses of a state plane coordinate system as maintained by the National Geodetic Survey;<hr><ltbullet>provides for continued recognition of prior systems for historical documents;<hr><ltbullet>requires use of the units as defined by the National Geodetic Survey;<hr><ltbullet>creates additional paths for licensure as a professional land surveyor; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
